<br>
PoP may introduce some new situations, some of which may require that players adapt to new settings/environments... but new tactics? Hmm.<br>
<br>
And while there are a few classes that do require a certain amount of skill to play, and there are also situations that can be resolved via the use of efficient tactics, the game does not require either of these for survival nearly so much as it requires good equipment. <br>
<br>
Small well-equiped groups who use &quot;tactics&quot; may be able to accomplish a great deal, but small poorly-equiped groups who use tactics? Serve as lunch more often than not.<br>
