<br>
It costs 12 AA to buy those 3 point.<br>
<br>
+1 mana regen for MC1.  Cost 2 AA.<br>
+1 mana regen for MC2.  Cost 4 AA.<br>
+1 mana regen for MC3.  Cost 6 AA.<br>
<br>
That's right, getting an additional +2 mana regen over MC1 costs a whopping 10 points.<br>
<br>
